data.description: Seeking tranquility and a break from the city rush? Revel in the vast expanse of open skies and serene surroundings. Here lies an opportunity to own a spacious property in the burgeoning area of Silver Springs. Nestled on 4.77 acres, this converted 3-bed, 2-bath manufactured home offers ample room for a family yearning for space. The property boasts mature trees gracing the front half, while the expansive back area provides the canvas for raising livestock, accommodating horses, or constructing a workshop. Just a brief 30-minute drive from Carson City and Fernley, and a scenic hour's journey from Lake Tahoe and Reno, Silver Springs epitomizes a tranquil, steadily growing community.  Enjoy swift access to the Industrial USA Parkway, making commuting effortless. This haven offers both the serenity of rural living and the convenience of nearby cities, presenting an ideal blend for those seeking a harmonious balance."
